CATEGORIES:TRC Durham
DESCRIPTION:Come and climb while the gym is closed to the public! Members 
 can bring one guest and it will not count against your monthly guest pass.
  Additional guests may visit by using your regular monthly guest pass\, fi
 rst time guest pass\, or with the purchase of a Day Pass. Rental gear will
  be provided for anyone using a guest pass and we&amp\;rsquo\;ll be runnin
 g complementary belay clinics for anyone who would like to learn how to to
 p-rope belay.
